**Connector metadata JSON schema:**
```json
{
  "version": "v1",
  "asset": {
    "name": "customers",
    "type": "table",  // or "view", "materialized_view", "file", "stream"
    "location": "s3://org-a-raw/customers.parquet",
    "format": "parquet",  // or "csv", "json", "avro", "delta"
    "row_count": 1000000,
    "size_bytes": 52428800,
    "created_at": "2026-01-10T10:00:00Z",
    "updated_at": "2026-01-12T08:00:00Z"
  },
  "schema": {
    "version": "v2.3",
    "hash": "abc123def456",  // MD5 of columns JSON
    "columns": [
      {
        "name": "customer_id",
        "type": "INTEGER",
        "nullable": false,
        "primary_key": true,
        "description": "Unique customer identifier"
      },
      {
        "name": "email",
        "type": "VARCHAR(255)",
        "nullable": true,
        "description": "Customer email address"
      },
      {
        "name": "created_at",
        "type": "TIMESTAMP",
        "nullable": false,
        "description": "Record creation timestamp"
      }
    ]
  },
  "lineage": {
    "upstream": [
      {
        "type": "s3_file",
        "location": "s3://org-a-raw/customers.csv",
        "last_modified": "2026-01-12T07:00:00Z"
      },
      {
        "type": "api",
        "source": "salesforce_api",
        "endpoint": "https://api.salesforce.com/v1/customers"
      }
    ],
    "transformation": {
      "type": "glue_crawler",  // or "dbt_model", "redshift_view", "lambda_etl"
      "job_id": "crawler-abc-123",
      "logic": "Discovered schema from parquet file",
      "config": {
        "crawler_name": "org-a-raw-crawler",
        "database": "org_a"
      }
    }
  },
  "quality": {
    "completeness": 0.92,
    "accuracy": 0.95,
    "null_counts": {
      "email": 50000
    },
    "duplicates": 10,
    "last_checked": "2026-01-12T08:00:00Z"
  },
  "governance": {
    "data_classification": "PII",  // Public, Internal, Confidential, PII
    "compliance_tags": ["GDPR", "HIPAA"],
    "business_owner": "jane@acme.com",
    "technical_steward": "john@acme.com",
    "business_purpose": "Customer master data for CRM",
    "retention_days": 365
  }
}
```

**GraphQL mutation spec:**
```graphql
mutation createDataAssetWithContext(
  $input: DataAssetContextInput!
) {
  createDataAssetWithContext(input: $input) {
    uuid
    name
    business_purpose
    quality_score
    schema_version
    lineage_summary {
      upstream_count
      downstream_count
    }
  }
}

input DataAssetContextInput {
  version: String!  # "v1"
  organization_id: ID!
  workspace_id: ID!
  asset: AssetInput!
  schema: SchemaInput
  lineage: LineageInput
  quality: QualityInput
  governance: GovernanceInput
}
```

**Implementation:**
- File: `/Users/bado/iccha/brighthive/brighthive-platform-core/src/graphql/resolvers/data-asset-resolver.ts`
- New mutation: `createDataAssetWithContext`
- Logic:
  1. Validate input (required fields, types)
  2. Create DataAsset node
  3. Create SchemaVersion node (if provided)
  4. Create lineage edges (if provided)
  5. Store quality metrics in DynamoDB (if provided)
  6. Create governance relationships (if provided)

**Versioning:**
- Version field in payload: "v1", "v2", etc.
- Backward compatibility: v1 supports minimal fields, v2 adds new fields
- Validation: reject unknown versions

